{"parentUuid":"154527d4-76bc-448e-b596-2bb76b46aa57","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/workspaces/agent-feed/prod","sessionId":"892909d3-aa5f-4e15-a679-572d401e85fb","version":"1.0.120","gitBranch":"v1","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-20250514","id":"msg_01SeG9nYomHVopq61s1FST2q","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Practical Applications\n\n### Quantum Computing\n- **Quantum Gates**: Entanglement enables quantum computers to perform calculations exponentially faster than classical computers for specific problems\n- **Quantum Algorithms**: Algorithms like Shor's (factoring) and Grover's (search) rely on entanglement\n\n### Quantum Communication\n- **Quantum Key Distribution (QKD)**: Uses entanglement to create unbreakable encryption keys\n- **Quantum Internet**: Future networks will use entangled particles for ultra-secure communication\n\n### Quantum Sensing\n- **Enhanced Precision**: Entangled particles can achieve measurement precision beyond classical limits\n- **Gravitational Wave Detection**: LIGO uses quantum entanglement principles for unprecedented sensitivity"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":393,"cache_read_input_tokens":42591,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":393,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CUabEcKfkfNaoW24nSXaA","type":"assistant","uuid":"a4576973-c379-40d1-9aa1-c47fb3ef9e72","timestamp":"2025-10-29T01:04:58.427Z"}
