{"parentUuid":"84ca8125-7a1a-418b-806f-3361bee5b950","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/workspaces/agent-feed/prod","sessionId":"892909d3-aa5f-4e15-a679-572d401e85fb","version":"1.0.120","gitBranch":"v1","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-20250514","id":"msg_01RLVbn2zPoA6U3wnZy3ZmoJ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Common Misconceptions\n\n### \"Information Travels Faster Than Light\"\n**Reality**: No information is transmitted between entangled particles. The correlation is instantaneous, but extracting meaningful information requires classical communication.\n\n### \"You Can Control One Particle by Measuring Another\"\n**Reality**: Measurement results are random. You cannot force a specific outcome by measuring the entangled partner.\n\n### \"Entanglement Enables Telepathy or Mind Control\"\n**Reality**: Entanglement is a purely physical phenomenon between particles, not a mechanism for transmitting thoughts or controlling minds.\n\n### \"Entanglement Violates Causality\"\n**Reality**: While correlations are instantaneous, no cause-and-effect relationship violates special relativity since no information travels faster than light."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":400,"cache_read_input_tokens":42984,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":400,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":6,"service_tier":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CUabF2wkjagUJTrfTgWKN","type":"assistant","uuid":"1659d750-0f1a-41a3-862d-c150ab15d736","timestamp":"2025-10-29T01:05:05.460Z"}
