{"parentUuid":"10565ba9-caa5-47b3-bd45-59e2dea22fc6","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/workspaces/agent-feed/prod","sessionId":"892909d3-aa5f-4e15-a679-572d401e85fb","version":"1.0.120","gitBranch":"v1","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-20250514","id":"msg_01SJNLvd3gCqkfkBfMHAP9v9","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## The Fundamental Mystery\n\nQuantum entanglement reveals the non-local nature of reality at the quantum scale. It shows that particles can be fundamentally connected in ways that classical physics cannot explain, yet this connection cannot be used to transmit information faster than light, preserving the structure of special relativity.\n\nThis phenomenon continues to drive both theoretical research into the foundations of quantum mechanics and practical developments in quantum technologies that promise to revolutionize computing, communication, and sensing in the coming decades."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":406,"cache_read_input_tokens":43384,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":406,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CUabFZDfRK8kRvJ72C9oC","type":"assistant","uuid":"3783ef84-6493-4436-a915-fefc0ea560f3","timestamp":"2025-10-29T01:05:11.381Z"}
